1 SUMMARY
22 This bill establishes municipal cost components for state and county services provided
33 to the unorganized territory that would normally be paid for by a municipality. The
44 municipal cost components constitute the property tax for the unorganized territory. The
55 bill also provides for a one-time prepayment in fiscal year 2025-26 to the unorganized
66 territories of Washington County and requires recovery of the prepayment through the
77 municipal cost component on or before June 30, 2027.
